      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=q6ap0a1psh]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=q6ap0a1psh]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=xam2gdk4rd]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xam2gdk4rd]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=oh19t9d7fu]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=oh19t9d7fu]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"q6ap0a1psh\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"xam2gdk4rd\">Captured by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://aversten.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peter Aversten</a></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"oh19t9d7fu\">Use</span></strong>: Attach this map to a PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/charles_xii_hdri/4562_charlesxii.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608534529/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285023763&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608534529/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285023763&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608534551\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608534529\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"49622633-761e-45e8-8a02-a7e93b5fdf3d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608534529/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285023763&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608534529/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285023763&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"CharlesXII-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>Location: The bedroom of Charles XII</p><p><em>Karl XII</em>; 17 June 1682 &ndash; 30 November 1718&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_XII_of_Sweden\" rel=\"nofollow\">King of Sweden</a>&nbsp;was put on display in this room after his death in Norway during a battle.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"charles_preview.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608534529/charles_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285104357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=380\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608534529/charles_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285104357&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"960\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=